
start with a promise - what people will know at the end of the hour that they didn't know before it. 
                       you could show an example of improvement that this knowlege will allow to achieve.

focus - show something that you need people to focus on, not more

cycle - repeat your idea multiple times, it's important.

verbal puncuation - pause so that people who've lost the thought catch up

you want the slides to be condiments to what you are saying, not the main event. 
